'''Obanta''' (yinkọ jọun etọn '''Ogborogan''') 
wẹ Ahọlu atọ̀ntọ to Ahọluduta Ijebu tọn mẹ he du to owhe-kanweko wiẹnẹtọ he wa lẹzun [[Ayimatẹn Ogun Tọn|Ayimatẹn Ogun tọn]], to [[Naijilia]].
Obanta nọ nukọnna gbẹtọ lẹ nado tọ́n sọ́n Ile Ife bo yi du Ahọlu to Ijebu Ode whenuena onọ̀ etọn sìn otọ́, Ahọlu (King) Olu Iwa, he yin Awujale Ijebu Ode tọn tintan basi matintọ.

 










